Description copied from interface: SharedContext
Add an outcomeContext to be executed on Vin side. RESTRICTION: if multiple OutcomeContext objects are added, it is the uptaker responsibility that there is only one per Vin instance provided. Vin does *not* support yet multiple outcome per Vin instance.

setWarningOnInterruption

public void setWarningOnInterruption(boolean warnOnInterruption)
Description copied from interface: SharedContext
Indicates if VIN needs to warn user when he tries to interrupt the action before its completion. To be called by the action implementer. Can be called multiple times during action execution to change the value at different stages of the action.

Specified by:
